Clean up the reject/copy to spambox/deliver to recipient options:

         R  C  P

-r       Y  -  -
none     N  Y  Y
-b       N  Y  N
default  N  N  Y
none     N  N  N

With the current flags there is no way to silently drop the mail or
both copy and deliver.
